Package burlap.shell.command.world

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddRelationSGCommand
    A ShellCommand for adding a relational target to an attribute for the current World State.
    AddStateObjectSGCommand
    A ShellCommand for adding an OO-MDP object to the current World State.
    GameCommand
    A ShellCommand for starting a game with the agents registered in a World.
    GenerateStateCommand
    A ShellCommand for generating a new state in a World according to the World's assigned SGStateGenerator.
    IsTerminalSGCommand
    A ShellCommand for checking whether the current world state is a terminal state or not.
    JointActionCommand
    A ShellCommand for manually setting and executing a JointAction for the shell's World.
    LastJointActionCommand
    A ShellCommand for printing the last joint action taken in a World.
    ManualAgentsCommands
    A controller for a set of ShellCommand objects.
    ManualAgentsCommands.ManualSGAgent  
    RemoveRelationSGCommand
    A ShellCommand for removing a relational target from an attribute for the current World State.
    RemoveStateObjectSGCommand
    A ShellCommand for removing an OO-MDP object from the current World State.
    RewardsCommand
    A ShellCommand for printing the last joint rewards delivered by a World.
    SetAttributeSGCommand
    A ShellCommand for setting attribute values for the current World State.
    WorldObservationCommand
    A ShellCommand for printing the current observation from the shell's World.
